## Frontend-only mode (D-W04)

When `has_backend=false` (no FastAPI), the web add-on is fully decoupled.
`API_BASE_URL` defaults to the `VITE_API_BASE_URL` environment variable:

```bash
# Point at your separately-deployed backend
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.yourservice.com pnpm dev
```

The `src/lib/api.ts` fetch wrapper reads `API_BASE_URL` from `@/config`,
so no code change is needed — just set the env var.

