## Adding more shadcn components

The 7 pre-vendored components (`button`, `card`, `input`, `label`,
`dialog`, `sheet`, `sonner`) live under `src/components/ui/`. Add more:

```bash
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add <component-name>
```

The `components.json` in this directory tells shadcn where to write new
components and which style / color system to use (Tailwind v4, OKLCH,
`cssVariables: true`).
